name booktabstabular
category Package
revision 79487
shortdesc Automatic application of the booktabs style
longdesc This package provides wrapper environments around tabular and
longdesc tabular* that insert \toprule at the beginning, \bottomrule at
longdesc the end, and locally remap the legacy \hline and \cline
longdesc commands to their booktabs equivalents \midrule and \cmidrule.
longdesc It also provides commands to temporarily override the standard
longdesc tabular and tabular* environments so that existing documents
longdesc can opt into this behaviour without rewriting each table.
